FIG. 2 is a cross sectional view taken along the line A--A in FIG. 1;


FIG. 3 is a cross sectional view taken along the line B--B in FIG. 1;


FIG. 4 is a cross sectional view taken along the line C--C in FIG. 1;


FIG. 5 is a block diagram showing a control system in the waste collection and treatment system as shown in FIG. 1;


FIG. 6 is a cross sectional view depicting a hopper installed in a sediment separation chamber as shown in FIG. 1;


FIGS. 7A and 7B are cross sectional views depicting a scum skimmer mechanism installed in the sediment separation chamber in FIG. 1; and


FIG. 8 is a top sectional view of a second embodiment of the waste collection and treatment system constructed in accordance with the principles of the present invention.
